data.description: Room for everyone!  This amazing home in an amazing location has it all!  Four bedrooms, study, game room, media room, covered patios and a three car garage! First floor is open, airy and has a kitchen we all desire with granite, tile black-splash and wood cabinets. The large sit at island is perfect for any baker needing counter space or to host extra seats for additional dining. Beautiful primary bedroom on the first floor is a retreat from a long day with a beautiful en-suite for anyone to relax in.  Home built on a premier large lot with lots of room to host gatherings and ready to be a gardener's delight.
